程序包 frogger.model

类 Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • frogger.model.Map
  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object

    Map

    The Map Class is used to contain all different types of Actor objects and provide the method for outside classes to access or add these objects.

    Use: 

                    Map map = new Map();
                map.getActor().add(.....);
    从以下版本开始:
    1.0
    版本:
    1.0
    作者:
    Wenzheng Shan
